segment.source: The log files for the Application Virtualization (App-V) Sequencer provide detailed information about sequencing applications, and they can be helpful when you are verifying functionality or when you are troubleshooting issues.
segment.target: The log files for the Application Virtualization (App-V) Sequencer provide detailed information about sequencing applications, and they can be helpful when you are verifying functionality or when you are troubleshooting issues.

segment.source: The following table provides information about the log files and their default locations, which are created when using the Sequencer.
segment.target: The following table provides information about the log files and their default locations, which are created when using the Sequencer.
